{"tid":1508994,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"之後既遊行除左美帝旗，仲應該整標語呼籲美國盡法通過人權及民主法案","createTime":"2019-08-26T16:34:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-01T16:37:37.000Z","uid":210140,"like":46,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":36,"replies":[{"pid":"53ed18969025426174486082417a9500faba863b","tid":1508994,"uid":210140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T16:34:32.000Z","msg":"最近先有兩個建制議員走去賣港<br />\n唔可以俾佢代表左全香港人<br />\n除左舉美帝旗外，一定要舉牌呼籲並支持呢條法案<br />\n雖然身為「出設天才」既我晨早買定左枝美帝旗到時舉，以免整埋Ｄ核突標語<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但都希望並呼籲大家咁做<br />\n<br />\nP.S.有四位泛民議員都有份去美國希望美國「不要制裁」香港，請盡選民責任，大家問清楚發生咩事<br />\n【逆權運動】鍾國斌引述美議員 或要檢視《香港政策法》<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1508311/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1508311/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"3ca40f903cb28c24fa4964693bd7bc4f9348e63d","tid":1508994,"uid":33930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T16:35:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9hjf7rg.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9hjf7rg.gif&h=994c84f5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n九月一號下午一點機場見<br />\n<br />\n901機場和你塞 Channel<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=qutgakuQBXsObMwiKtfrsfUf%2F0pSCBsIIvLsnv1ZXiY%3D&h=e777da09\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyou</a><br />\n901機場和你塞 公海<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyouopen\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyouopen&d=qutgakuQBXsObMwiKtfrsfUf%2F0pSCBsIIvLsnv1ZXiY%3D&h=8e778fa5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyouopen</a><br />\n901機場和你塞 宣傳<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyoupromote\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyoupromote&d=qutgakuQBXsObMwiKtfrsfUf%2F0pSCBsIIvLsnv1ZXiY%3D&h=79776260\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyoupromote</a>"},{"pid":"ac62f955c1ba1b34e927eea458